ive aspects that can lead to\nunprecedented schemes for strong light-matter interaction, slow and confined\nlight.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Nov 2017 17:32:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
