effectively in the presence of diffuse emission. Extensions of this method are\ndirectly applicable to other upcoming radio surveys such as the POlarization\nSky Survey of the Universe's Magnetism (POSSUM) with the Australia Square\nKilometre Array Pathfinder (ASKAP), and the SKA itself.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Nov 2017 10:56:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
