nmental effects resulting from its nuclear\nlocation. Remarkably, we also discovered that PS1-10adi is not an isolated\ncase. We therefore surmise that this new population of transients has\npreviously been overlooked due to incorrect association with underlying central\nblack hole activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Nov 2017 13:37:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
